snippet.title: GAZZLERS - Release Date Reveal | Meta Quest, Pico, PS VR2 & Steam VR
snippet.description:
GAZZLERS is out on SEPTEMBER 14th on Meta Quest, Pico, PS VR2 & Steam. 

Wishlist or pre-order now: https://gazzlers.com/linktree

GAZZLERS is an insane VR shooter full of diesel-fueled chaos! Embark on an epic journey across the lands of Ginkgo and build awesome weapons to face hordes of crazy enemies in search of the Final Station. Will you be able to complete the Pilgrimage of Steel?

#metaquest #pico #playstationvr2 #steam #gamescom2023
